accessibility.text: What if the white petal is at the bottom?
What if the white petal is at the bottom?
R2 will move it to the top
If the top petal position is already taken, rotate the top (U) until the petal position is available
What if the white petal is at the bottom?
R2 will move it to the top
If the top petal position is already taken, rotate the top (U) until the petal position is available
Tips: Keep the solved pieces in place once they’re in their correct positions.
